Diamond Platnumz caused a furore after his message wishing his son a happy birthday rubbed women the wrong way. The bongo star started off by saying his responsibility to Prince Nillan is only to get him lots of money so that Nillan will never lack. What angered many was his words where he told his son ‘awatembezee‘ and ‘apite nao’. nauratapple: Mtoto afundishwe maadili mema.
